<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>One-Time Password</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h1>One-Time Password (OTP)</h1>
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>Here is your one-time password (OTP) for authentication:</p>
        <div style="
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        ">
            {{otp}}
        </div>
        <p>This one-time password will expire in {{expirationMinutes}} minutes.</p>
        <p>If you did not request this OTP, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>